{"tid":1738424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一張圖話你知，炳強呢條友係冷血，嚟緊拉人數字一定再直線升","createTime":"2019-11-19T08:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:37:45.000Z","uid":161430,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34902aa23a28e1d468b1fce1e906cb9b0c662d27","tid":1738424,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"記唔記得當年深水埗地鐵站有單女警開槍案，隻差婆開槍射傷個地裝修佬。(其實只係一年前)<br />\n<br />\n當年連登仔拗呢單嘢拗到面紅耳赤，但最大問題唔係呢度，而係誰對誰錯，其實呢單都係一單悲劇，無論點都係有個人返工途中比人用實彈射啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181108/_2018110814053580456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181108%2F_2018110814053580456.jpg&h=9221a5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當時炳強事後就專登去搵隻差婆，好似贏咗場交咁，好威咁同開槍嘅人樹起手指公影去大合照，你覺得咁嘅人心地可以好得去邊？正常嘅同理心呢？<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅人而家做埋處長，大家唔需要驚，不過當然要小心，冷血嘅人做處長，落order都會係冷血，之後拉人數字肯定會再直線爆上，肯定之後有實彈shoot to kill，嚟緊要有心理準備"},{"pid":"c21b362306068eb1c08d547f2dec0ad15e966893","tid":1738424,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:52:26.000Z","msg":"721 鄧炳強 唔見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ddc4732ef38ff86910f732a6b570380c4aadd3","tid":1738424,"uid":276150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"未撚驚過，遺書都寫定，呢條冚家剷唔好諗住靠嚇，橫死掂死嘅啫！"},{"pid":"87b96a2fad460bf855d83042c897e1c5d66bef76","tid":1738424,"uid":140666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"佢仲係CU 社工出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6651852d6e21388f8c721ad7c47920c775d65828","tid":1738424,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72abd1fa748958ccf7a0ed3e14cbebfbe5992ce","tid":1738424,"uid":259613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強<br />\nTang Ping Keung<br />\n私人電郵：carriechrischloe@hotmail.com<br />\n手提電話：66801551<br />\n出生日期：1965Jul4<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4/7/1965<br />\nFlat G 9/F Block 1<br />\nBoland Court 10-12 Broadcast Drive"},{"pid":"ec6a5d2e2d41c3f68e30b8a5627b794496e8f8c8","tid":1738424,"uid":292119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"回到60年代 黑警蹤橫黑白兩道⋯"},{"pid":"603c74a4bb9eb29b69a92ec2beb7182437114e31","tid":1738424,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/893311/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/893311/page/1</a><br />\n依單？當時我開過post話警權過大可以隨便使用致命武力，個個連登仔屌鳩我"},{"pid":"cdde577d2c491c72d0da51490fb7501f467e9095","tid":1738424,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"facebook行動 ＋ 區選前幫黃藍經濟圈收料<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741135</a>"}]}